refentry.refsect1:
&reftitle.description;
stringfalseopenssl_spki_new OpenSSLAsymmetricKeyprivate_key stringchallenge intdigest_algoOPENSSL_ALGO_MD5
使用指定散列算法生成新的签名公钥和 challenge。

&reftitle.changelog;





    &Version;
    &Description;





    8.0.0

     private_key 现在接受 OpenSSLAsymmetricKey
     实例；之前接受类型 OpenSSL key 的 &resource;。

  &reftitle.examples;

   openssl_spki_new 示例


     使用默认的摘要算法（MD5）生成新的 SPKAC



<?php
$pkey = openssl_pkey_new('secret password');
$spkac = openssl_spki_new($pkey, 'testing');

if ($spkac !== NULL) {
    echo $spkac;
} else {
    echo "SPKAC generation failed";
}
?>


